reacthooks
-useState = lets us track state
-useRef = control to get DOM elements when other means are not so straight forward
-useEffect = clean way to set things when component start and finish

-useContext = to pass config data down he component tree withput prop drilling
-useReducer = to oraganize out state management 
-useCallback = performance gain by not re re-rendering on every button click
-useMemo = to cache some data on client


